name: carl-olsen/brutal-helm
description: Long horns on each side of this helmet.

name: carl-olsen/crossbow
description: The Middle-Ages version of automatic riffles is much more powerful than a simple bow.

name: carl-olsen/flame
description: Dancing flames over the shadow.

name: carl-olsen/mite-alt
description: A friendly bug living in your cabinet.

name: carl-olsen/spider-alt
description: Placing webs in every corner to capture small insects for dinner.

name: carl-olsen/spider-face
description: Staring at you during your sleep.

name: cathelineau/annexation
description:
All your bases belong to us!
A military invasion in an enemy country to take it under permanent control.

name: cathelineau/bad-gnome
description: An evil ball of fur with a mask and a cap.

name: cathelineau/battleship
description: A heavy armored warship navigating the seven seas.

name: cathelineau/boar-ensign
description: A wild pig emblem

name: cathelineau/carnyx
description: Gallic trumpet designed to howl a disturbing war-song.

name: cathelineau/carrier
description: A floating military airport which serves as a tactical advanced position.

name: cathelineau/chariot
description: A light vehicle pulled by horses in epic races on sand tracks.

name: cathelineau/cruiser
description: A medium recognition frigate with a few cannons with a few cannons.

name: cathelineau/dread
description: Intense fear about a danger.

name: cathelineau/dreadnought
description: A massive battleship from the Royal Navy.

name: cathelineau/earth-worm
description: The small and gooey invertebrate living in moist underground doesn't want to go fishing.

name: cathelineau/flying-trout
description: When you are both a bird and a fish and you're comfortable with it.

name: cathelineau/fomorian
description: Ancient and hideous folk haunting cemeteries like zombies. They will remain lonely souls for eternity.

name: cathelineau/great-war-tank
description: A heavy armored tank on the battlefield.

name: cathelineau/holy-oak
description: That tree is a sacred one, see it shining. Druids and elves will pray at this sacred place to gather mana.

name: cathelineau/iron-hulled-warship
description: Ironclads are ancient steam propelled ships with heavy armor and big sails.

name: cathelineau/medusa-head
description: Dozen of snakes are swarming the crown of this petrifying Gorgon, that can turn the victims into stone.

name: cathelineau/nun-face
description: A religious Sister.

name: cathelineau/occupy
description: The siege is over. Tanks are spreading through the city streets that had surrendered.

name: cathelineau/old-king
description: This old leader relies on wisdom and strength to rule his kingdom.

name: cathelineau/oppidum
description: Gallic cities were on top of hills between wood walls.

name: cathelineau/polar-bear
description: A white bear living in Arctic areas, near the North Pole. It mainly eat fish to survive.

name: cathelineau/swordman
description: A fighter with blade and shield.

name: cathelineau/swordwoman
description: A female fighter in the rage of a battle.

name: cathelineau/torc
description: A twisted necklace very hard to remove.

name: cathelineau/transparent-slime
description: A jelly creature with no opacity that can flatten itself to pass underneath low obstacle.

name: cathelineau/tree-face
description: Wooden mask carved in the trunk of an old tree. The hollow eyes and mouth may be filled with magic items.

name: cathelineau/tumulus
description: Ancient respected warchiefs were buried in huge handmade hills.

name: cathelineau/witch-face
description: An old and ugly shrew living in a dirty shack in the deep forest, mixing magic potions.

name: catsu/broken-arrow
description: This arrow is shattered like glass.

name: darkzaitzev/acrobatic
description: Quick agile moves in the air, harmoniously jumping from ropes, cables or small platforms.

name: darkzaitzev/apothecary
description: Large bowl to prepare mixtures and medicines by combining herbs and special potions.

name: darkzaitzev/big-gear
description: This massive cog is tough enough to rotate inside battleship mechanical engines.

name: darkzaitzev/catch
description: You need good reflexes and grip to catch this thrown stick in mid-air with your bare hands.

name: darkzaitzev/cauldron
description: To boil weird liquid preparations, like mana soup or melted frog juice with cinnamon.

name: darkzaitzev/chameleon-glyph
description: This master of disguise of the animal reign curls tightly when it needs to rest.

name: darkzaitzev/death-juice
description: Drop from the after-world. At first it may be confused with blood or bone marrow.

name: darkzaitzev/distraction
description: Hard to stay focus on a task when something else very interesting occurs around.

name: darkzaitzev/fish-cooked
description: A salmon on a stick over a campfire. It's less sweet than marshmallow but give more energy.

name: darkzaitzev/flying-shuriken
description: Like a metal falcon approaching it's prey at high speed.

name: darkzaitzev/fried-fish
description: With French fries and a bit of lemon juice, this anchovy or herring will be a salty meal.

name: darkzaitzev/hooded-assassin
description: The dagger of this murderer is ready to dive deep in the heart of the victim during this occult ceremony.

name: darkzaitzev/hooded-figure
description: This mysterious being hidden under a large cloak runs swiftly through the twilight. It may be a ranger or an elf.

name: darkzaitzev/kusarigama
description: This chain-sickle is a sharp traditional Japanese weapon used during the Middle Ages.

name: darkzaitzev/ninja-head
description: Only the eyes are visible behind this mask. This way there's no way to recognize the assassin.

name: darkzaitzev/ninja-heroic-stance
description: This Asian warrior is about to confront its worst opponents and enter the scene in a dramatic way.

name: darkzaitzev/north-star-shuriken
description: When you see it in the night sky, it may be too late for you.

name: darkzaitzev/on-sight
description: That is a scary situation when someone is aiming at you with a sniper rifle and you can't move.

name: darkzaitzev/plants-and-animals
description: A snake surrounding a young crop. Symbol of harmony between fauna and flora in nature.

name: darkzaitzev/ram
description: This goat like animal stinks a lot and hit very hard with the huge horns on the top of its head.

name: darkzaitzev/revolt
description: Ready to go on strike by mobilizing the angry mob and fight against the government.

name: darkzaitzev/robber-hand
description: This nice purse full of coins is a temptation that a thief can't resist to steal.

name: darkzaitzev/running-ninja
description: This dark shadow was jumping from roof to roof before it dashes in a desert alley.

name: darkzaitzev/severed-hand
description: Those five fingers are no longer connected to the rest of the arm. In the separating process, the watch has been lost.

name: darkzaitzev/sharp-shuriken
description: This rotating razor can fit in a small bag. So you can carry a lot.

name: darkzaitzev/shuriken
description: Small metal star, spinning in the air until it reaches a soft target and remain stuck.

name: darkzaitzev/skull-sabertooth
description: This long teeth had made big damages while they were attached to a living head.

name: darkzaitzev/smoke-bomb
description: For a quick evasion, this ball emits large amount of opaque gas that blinds enemies.

name: darkzaitzev/star-shuriken
description: Simple spinning star used during martial art combats.

name: darkzaitzev/tabi-boot
description: Light shoes with no hard sole producing loud noises. This way discretion is optimal.

name: darkzaitzev/three-pointed-shuriken
description: Three blades are interconnected in the center by a metal ring. But it can only follow one path.

name: darkzaitzev/whirlpool-shuriken
description: Like a small tornado made of blades that could also be taken from a power tool saw.

name: delapouite/3d-glasses
description:
Red and blue filters to experience movies with extra dimensions thanks to stereoscopy.
In the cinema, hard to tell which objects are real and which ones simple pop out of the theater screen.

name: delapouite/3d-hammer
description: To hit on metal in a forge and produce perfect blades.

name: delapouite/3d-meeple
description: A small wooden character used as tokens by each player. This placeholder is placed on a board to show the game progress.

name: delapouite/3d-stairs
description: A staircase to reach the deeper level of a dungeon or, on the contrary, escape from the darkness one step at the time.

name: delapouite/abacus
description: Wooden balls used to count or tally before computers and their infinite power over numbers were everywhere.

name: delapouite/abbot-meeple
description: A monk in charge of sharing the holy knowledged to surrounding folks.

name: delapouite/achilles-heel
description:
This kind of non obvious weak point can turn into a crucial vulnerability when discovered.
At least it's not an arrow in the knee!

name: delapouite/acoustic-megaphone
description: Simple way to scream loudly to a crowd during a strike to give it instructions or orders.

name: delapouite/africa
description: This continent is considered the crib of mankind. The north part is covered by the Sahara desert. Below, the savanna is home of many species like lions, giraffes and elephants.

name: delapouite/agave
description: This dry plant growing in the desert is used to produce Tequila.

name: delapouite/ages
description: An adult and a child side by side. One person is old and wise, the other one is young and quick.

name: delapouite/air-balloon
description: Hot and slow balloon to travel in the clouds and go around the world in less than 80 days.

name: delapouite/airplane-arrival
description: After a long flight, this plane is finally landing on the airport.

name: delapouite/airplane-departure
description: Take off to reach the clouds and start a journey.

name: delapouite/airtight-hatch
description: This pressurized environment rely on a thick automated seal to protect the inside from the void.

name: delapouite/akhet
description: A hieroglyph representing the sun rising over a mountain.

name: delapouite/alarm-clock
description: Produces a strident ring to wake you up in the morning. If the hands are not phosphorescent, it's impossible to tell the time in dark room at night.

name: delapouite/algae
description: Aquatic plants living on rocks at the bottom of the ocean. It's often a shelter for fish and can even be turned into an edible salad.

name: delapouite/algeria
description: Country located north of Africa, on the south bank of the Mediterannean sea.

name: delapouite/alien-bug
description: An insectoid alien living in swarm colony and multiplying at big scale in no time.

name: delapouite/alien-egg
description: A monstrous baby about to emerge from its viscous incubation cocoon and start hunting.

name: delapouite/all-seeing-eye
description: The Eye of providence casting rays. God is watching you, even from dollar bills.

name: delapouite/almond
description: A dry nut used to make milk, cake and biscuits like nougat or macarons.

name: delapouite/amber-mosquito
description: A disturbing blood sucker from Jurassic trapped in stone. It contains previous DNA necessary to bring back to life extinct species like dinosaurs.

name: delapouite/ambulance
description: An emergency transportation to carry injured people to the nearest hospital in a hurry.

name: delapouite/american-football-ball
description: Give it to the quarterback to score. The rugby ball is quite similar, looking like a long egg.

name: delapouite/american-football-helmet
description: To protect the quaterback's head when the ball is dropping.

name: delapouite/american-football-player
description: A light armor is necessary to run across the field as a quarterback.

name: delapouite/american-shield
description: Made from Vibranium, the Captain's shield is virtually indestructible and usually comes back like a Frisbee.

name: delapouite/amphora
description: A Roman vase to hold wine or other precious liquids during banquets. Many fragments of amphora are found in archaeological site.

name: delapouite/ample-dress
description: A large skirt that may be worn during a wedding or a ceremony.

name: delapouite/anarchy
description: A political movement against establishment where decisions follow the will of the people.

name: delapouite/ancient-columns
description: 3 broken columns belonging to an old temple in ruins.

name: delapouite/ancient-ruins
description: An old temple falling apart with broken columns and rusty parts.

name: delapouite/ancient-screw
description: This bolt belongs to the carapace to old guardian robots.

name: delapouite/ancient-sword
description: This old sword is stuck in a stone and covered with moss.

name: delapouite/angola
description:
South african country bordered by the Atlantic Ocean.
The capital is Luanda.

name: delapouite/angry-eyes
description: Stare with frowned eyebrows, feeling anger.

name: delapouite/animal-hide
description:
Leather skin, gathered after hunting or farming.
This nice fur can then be turned into a pelt.

name: delapouite/ant
description: A small part of a coordinated crowd.

name: delapouite/antarctica
description: The frozen continent at the South Pole is full of mysteries under the thick ice.

name: delapouite/antibody
description: The immune system used this Y-shaped protein produced by plasma cells to neutralize pathogens like bacteria and viruses

name: delapouite/anticlockwise-rotation
description: An arrow turning from right to left in the top quadrant.

name: delapouite/ants
description: A colony of soldiers and workers contributing to the hive.

name: delapouite/anubis
description: Egyptian god of mummification with a jackal head, which looks like a wolf like invincible monster.

name: delapouite/apollo-capsule
description: A lunar module designed to carry astronauts back on earth.

name: delapouite/apple-core
description: This apple has been eaten and only the center remains with seeds.

name: delapouite/aquarium
description: A fish tank with a small bubbling goldfish swimming around endlessly. It waits for magic food falling from above.

name: delapouite/aquarius
description: A goddess pouring mighty water star constellation - Zodiacal sign from January to February

name: delapouite/aqueduct
description: Roman bridge transporting water across long distances to fill reservoirs.

name: delapouite/arabic-door
description: The beautifully decorated entrance of an Arabic temple, with colorful mosaic tiles.

name: delapouite/arc-triomphe
description: Famous monument of Paris, at the top of the Champs-Élysées on la Place de l'Étoile.

name: delapouite/arch-bridge
description: The big pillars of this structure enhance the balance of the arch.

name: delapouite/archer
description: Calm and concentration must be mastered to aim in the bull eyes.

name: delapouite/archive-research
description: Mysteries are hidden in these pages, a scholar exploring the library should be able to find them.

name: delapouite/aries
description: Ram star constellation - Zodiacal sign from March to April

name: delapouite/arm-bandage
description: An injury between the elbow and the shoulder, with straps to avoid infection.

name: delapouite/arm-sling
description: This injury at the broken elbow needs a plaster to full recovery.

name: delapouite/arm
description: Superior limb with the hand at one end and the shoulder at the other one with the biceps in between.

name: delapouite/armadillo
description: This stripped animal from America has a leather armor shell and can morph into a defensive ball.

name: delapouite/armor-downgrade
description: Defense decreasing, more vulnerability to expect.

name: delapouite/armor-punch
description: A metal fist in a gauntlet hitting at full speed.

name: delapouite/armor-upgrade
description: Defense increasing, more protection. Immunity has been granted thanks to this power-up.

name: delapouite/armored-boomerang
description: Try to hunt a heavy kangaroo with it to see if it goes back to you.

name: delapouite/arrest
description: A bad guy under arrest by the police who must show his empty hands and obey the orders. Or it could be a threatened hostage.

name: delapouite/arrow-cursor
description: Guide this pointer on the screen by moving the mouse. Then click to trigger an action on the graphical interface.

name: delapouite/arrow-wings
description: This arrow belongs to the bow of cupidon, it has an autopilot system.

name: delapouite/ascending-block
description: Big stone block being pulled along a slope to build a pyramid. No slaves involved.

name: delapouite/asian-lantern
description: Warm but soft light shining from this paper box with inscriptions.

name: delapouite/asparagus
description: A vegetable crop also called sparrow grass.

name: delapouite/aspergillum
description: A metal stick used by priests to sprinkle holy water during ceremonies.

name: delapouite/asteroid
description: A big rock floating in space that should not smash anything. There's a high concentration of them between Mars and Jupiter.

name: delapouite/astronaut-helmet
description: To let cosmonauts breath in the void and protect their brain from deadly space rays.

name: delapouite/atlas
description: Titan god of endurance and astronomy doomed to carry the globe on its shoulders, in an infinite torment.

name: delapouite/atom-core
description: Electrons rotating around a nucleus made of protons and neutrons.

name: delapouite/attached-shield
description: When you receive a blow on the other side, you better grab it forcefully to defend your life.

name: delapouite/audio-cassette
description: Magnetic tape from the 80s to record analog music on both faces and play it in a Walkman.

name: delapouite/australia
description: Big island or continent? It was the last huge land conquered by colonists against native aboriginal people.

name: delapouite/avocado
description: A big berry with one seed used to produce guacamole.

name: delapouite/avoidance
description: The collision was avoided by bending the trajectories.

name: delapouite/axe-in-log
description: A lumberjack is having a break after the tree is on down the forest floor on all branches have been stripped.

name: delapouite/axe-sword
description: Symbol of lumberjack warriors.

name: delapouite/azul-flake
description: This symbol is printed on top of light blue Azuleros.

name: delapouite/baby-bottle
description: Good milk when mum can't naturally feed the starving kid.

name: delapouite/baby-face
description: A toothless smile from a young child, amazed by everything's going on in the surroundings.

name: delapouite/babyfoot-players
description: Rows of metal soldiers kicking in a ball on a miniature soccer field. This is the kind of game found in bars.

name: delapouite/backgammon
description: Roll the dice to move the checker on the correct triangles.

name: delapouite/backpack
description: Huge bag with lots of pockets to carry the whole objects inventory and common equipment during a hiking trip.

name: delapouite/backward-time
description: This clock is going in the counter-clockwise direction, which means it travels to the past.

name: delapouite/bacon
description: Two stripes of salt-cured pork from parts with a lot of fat.

name: delapouite/bad-breath
description: Horrible odor coming from a zombie teeth made of rotten food or organs decomposition.

name: delapouite/ball-pyramid
description: A stack of spheres that remain in perfect balance. It also looks like a pool game seen from above.

name: delapouite/ballerina-shoes
description: Pointy light shoes for star dancers during ballets at the opera. Need strong toes to keep the balance.

name: delapouite/balloon-dog
description: This brittle and temporary creation fears spikes and strong winds. These kind of balloons often belon to clowns.

name: delapouite/bamboo-fountain
description: A quiet water tap in Asian gardens around ponds. Every few seconds the tube is filled and the liqud is poured in a bigger recipient.

name: delapouite/bamboo
description: Fast growing wooden tubes exploited for constructions.

name: delapouite/banana-bunch
description: A trio of juicy yellow bananas ready to be harvest. Cook them to produce a mighty meal, like in the Yiga Clan recipe.

name: delapouite/banana-peel
description:
A slippery skin on the floor is a frightening hazard.
During a Mario Kart race, banana peels are often left on the track by Donkey Kong and non attentive drivers skid out of the stage.

name: delapouite/banana-peeled
description: The peel has been removed and it's ready to be eaten as a dessert.

name: delapouite/banana
description: Tropical fruit long and yellow, loved by monkeys. Some people also called them plantains.

name: delapouite/bandit
description: A villain hiding its face behind a kerchief, about to rob a bank or a coach.

name: delapouite/banging-gavel
description: At the tribunal court, the verdict can't be pronounced if the crowd is noisy.

name: delapouite/bank
description: Safe place to store money and credits. Despite heavy protection by the police, banks are often the target of robberies and hold-ups.

name: delapouite/banknote
description: Money printed on paper for different amounts. Banknotes are lighter than their equivalents in coins.

name: delapouite/barbarian
description: A muscular warrior that may go berserk during battles. This kind of brutal man looks like a hero but is often outwitted by his opponents.

name: delapouite/barbecue
description: To cook meat outdoor in the garden during a week-end party. It needs the right sauce to get even tastier.

name: delapouite/barn
description: Warehouse to store sacks of grain, crops, haystacks or agricultural tractors in a farm.

name: delapouite/barracks-tent
description: Temporary place to rest or plan the next strategic move when on the battlefield.

name: delapouite/barracks
description: Infantry's living place in training camps. Inside, bunk beds are organized in rows like soldiers waiting quietly in their garrison.

name: delapouite/barrel-leak
description: A suspicious content escaping the open barrel is forming a puddle with disastrous environmental consequences.

name: delapouite/barrel
description: Big cylindrical alcohol container made of wood. It gives a special taste to the wine and whisky inside.

name: delapouite/barricade
description: A pile of street furniture and barbed wire to protect citizens during strikes and block infantry.

name: delapouite/barrier
description: It's forbidden to cross this fence and follow this path.

name: delapouite/baseball-bat
description: Wave this wooden stick to hit the ball and score home-runs during a game. This is also the weapon of choice against burglars.

name: delapouite/baseball-glove
description: To catch the ball during a game and avoid a home run.

name: delapouite/basketball-ball
description: Score points in the NBA championship by throwing this ball in the opponent basket.

name: delapouite/basketball-basket
description: Net to score 2 or 3 points depending of the zone.

name: delapouite/basketball-jersey
description: A light shirt with a number on it to distinguish players during a match.

name: delapouite/bastet
description: A cat statue with a large necklace and sitting in a noble attitude.

name: delapouite/bat-mask
description: A super hero living in the darkness and talking with a loud voice.

name: delapouite/bat
description: A flying fox living in dark caves. It sleeps upside down and use strident sounds to find its direction.

name: delapouite/bathtub
description: Clean your dirty body in the warmth of the bathroom.

name: delapouite/battle-mech
description: A giant metal robot with no apparent weapons but a strong armor to tank through enemy lines.

name: delapouite/beach-ball
description: Big inflatable balloon with stripes to play near the seashore during summer holidays.

name: delapouite/beach-bucket
description: Plastic tools used by kids to build sand castle during summer.

name: delapouite/beam-satellite
description: An orbit laser striking energy to specific military targets on Earth.

name: delapouite/bear-head
description: A strong and ferocious grizzly that can fish with its bare paws.

name: delapouite/beaver
description: A large aquatic rodent known to build dams over rivers.

name: delapouite/bed-lamp
description: A simple lamp to read good old books during evenings just before getting really sleepy.

name: delapouite/bed

name: delapouite/crime-scene-tape

name: delapouite/croissant

name: delapouite/crook-flail

name: delapouite/cross-shield

name: delapouite/crosscut-saw

name: delapouite/crosshair

name: delapouite/crossroad

name: delapouite/crow-nest
description: Lookout at the top of the main mast on a ship before radar was invented.

name: delapouite/crucifix
description: Holy symbol of a dying Jesus Christ to keep away vampires.

name: delapouite/cryo-chamber

name: delapouite/crystal-earrings

name: delapouite/cupcake

name: delapouite/curling-stone

name: delapouite/custodian-helmet

name: delapouite/cut-lemon

name: delapouite/cyber-eye

name: delapouite/cyborg-face

name: delapouite/cycling
description: Riding a bike during a race or simply for leisure.

name: delapouite/daemon-pull
description: A deadly grasp from the dark corner of the abyss.

name: delapouite/dagger-rose

name: delapouite/dam

name: delapouite/dandelion-flower
description: A big yellow flower with flying seeds in the wind.

name: delapouite/dango
description: Japanese dumpling made of rice flour and served with green tea.

name: delapouite/dart

name: delapouite/database
description: A silo containing precious data that can be queried.

name: delapouite/dead-head
description: A blank stare with the tongue outside the mouth.

name: delapouite/deer-track
description: A hunter can rely on these marks on the ground to follow the game.

name: delapouite/defense-satellite

name: delapouite/delivery-drone
description: A small flying helicopter in charge of carrying small packages.

name: delapouite/desert
description: Very hot nothingness covered with burning sand until the horizon with only a few cactus and no drinkable water.

name: delapouite/deshret-red-crown
description: Pharaohs of Lower Egypt have a rearing cobra as a symbol.

name: delapouite/desk
description: A working table in an office with a computer monitor on top.

name: delapouite/detour

name: delapouite/devil-mask
description: The Dark Lord from Hell awaits with its pitchfork.

name: delapouite/diamond-hilt

name: delapouite/diamond-ring
description: Piece of metal to give to your lover's finger.

name: delapouite/dice-fire
description: A burning dice when luck is on your side and you're about to score a bonus.

name: delapouite/dice-shield
description: This dice offers a buff in the defense stat. Better protection is always a nice bonus to obtain.

name: delapouite/dice-target
description: The right number has to appear on the dice if you want to reach your bonus goal.

name: delapouite/dice-twenty-faces-one
description: This dice is symbol of very bad luck.

name: delapouite/dice-twenty-faces-twenty
description: A D20

name: delapouite/dig-hole
description: Bury a victim in the ground or find a treasure. Who knows your real purpose when you dig a deep tunnel?

name: delapouite/dimetrodon
description:
A big lizard-like creature with a massive crest on its back.
This dinosaur cousin is not too distant from current Komodo dragons.
Beware, despite its appearance, it's more related to mammals than reptiles (Thanks Evan ;) )

name: delapouite/diplodocus
description: One of the biggest dinosaurs with a very long neck. It was an herbivore like actual graphs.

name: delapouite/diploma
description: A beautiful piece of paper attached on the wall, symbol of a success, like in school, at work or in sports.

name: delapouite/direction-sign
description: Indication to find a specific place along a path or a road.

name: delapouite/direction-signs
description: Which way to go? On the left of the road or on the right path?

name: delapouite/director-chair
description: When actors or directors need to rest on a set during shooting of a big movie for the cinema.

name: delapouite/disc-golf-bag

name: delapouite/disc-golf-basket

name: delapouite/discussion

name: delapouite/distress-signal

name: delapouite/diving-helmet
description: Headgear from a scuba equipment to breath underwater. Kind of the mask of Big Daddy in Bioshock.

name: delapouite/djinn
description: A spirit trapped in a lamp found in the desert. It can grant 3 wishes.

name: delapouite/dog-bowl
description: Dogs deserve a good meal too!

name: delapouite/dog-house
description: A small shed that serves as a kennel to shelter dogs in the garden.

name: delapouite/dolmen
description: A crude temple to old Gods, like StoneEdge or Carnac.

name: delapouite/dolphin

Clever animals living in playful bands under the waves of oceans.
Dolphins communicate and guide themselves with sophisticated ultrasounds, like Echo in the famous Sega title.

name: delapouite/domino-tiles
description: Like dies, number must be correctly align to build the full path.

name: delapouite/donut
description: A cake in a ring shape with chocolate or syrup on top.

name: delapouite/door-handle
description: If you have the correct key you may pass this entrance.

name: delapouite/door-ring-handle
description: This iron handle is heavy enough to produce a distinc knocking noise when hitting the door.

name: delapouite/door
description: A mobile separation between two rooms.

name: delapouite/double-fish
description: 2 fish quietly swimming in undisturbed water.

name: delapouite/double-street-lights
description: During the night, a dim light is always needed to feel safe.

name: delapouite/dough-roller
description:
Cuisine utensil used to flatten dough and prepare cakes or pizzas.
It's possible that cooks use this as a weapon during a fight in a bakery.

name: delapouite/dragon-orb
description: A mystic diviniation sphere resting in a reptilian palm.

name: delapouite/dragon-shield
description:
Can this protection sustain the fire-breath of a dragon?
Only a mighty adventurer may prove it.

name: delapouite/drakkar-dragon
description: A threatening mythical animal head with horns carved in the wood of a Viking ship bow.

name: delapouite/drakkar
description:
Viking ship with a fearsome dragon at the front and shields along the sides.
This is the kind of boat this fierce people used to invade French Normandy and even discover Canada.

name: delapouite/drawbridge

name: delapouite/dream-catcher

name: delapouite/drill
description: To push a screw into a wall or a plank without effort.

name: delapouite/drinking
description: Swallow large gulps of liquid to refresh your body. If it's alcohol the side effect can be troubling.

name: delapouite/drop-earrings
description: Round and shiny metal parts to go with an appropriate necklace.

name: delapouite/drum
description: Percussion instrument played with two sticks and marking the adequate tempo during military marches.

name: delapouite/duck-palm
description: This webbed foot is useful to propel on a liquid surface.

name: delapouite/duck

name: delapouite/duffel-bag

name: delapouite/dunce-cap

name: delapouite/dungeon-light

name: delapouite/duration
description: Only a few precious seconds left to end the game.

name: delapouite/dutch-bike

name: delapouite/dwarf-face

name: delapouite/dynamite

name: delapouite/eagle-head

name: delapouite/earrings
description: Two long metal plates with diamonds to wear with a necklace.

name: delapouite/earth-africa-europe
description: Our planet centered on the Birth and Old Continents

name: delapouite/earth-america
description: Our planet centered on the New World

name: delapouite/earth-asia-oceania
description: Our planet centered on the East, Australia and the archipels.

name: delapouite/easter-egg

name: delapouite/eating-pelican

name: delapouite/eating

name: delapouite/ecology
description: Protection of the environment with clean energies and good practices to reduce global warming.

name: delapouite/eel
description: This aquatic snake like fish may fight against a lamprey.

name: delapouite/egg-eye
description: A crack in the shell let the curious stare of a new born exploring the surroundings.

name: delapouite/egypt

North African country encompassing the Nile delta. It used to be the kingdom of Pharaohs.
The capital is Cairo.

name: delapouite/egyptian-urns

name: delapouite/eight-ball

name: delapouite/elbow-pad

name: delapouite/electrical-resistance

name: delapouite/electrical-socket
description: Holes in the wall to connect plugs of appliances.

name: delapouite/elevator

name: delapouite/elf-ear

name: delapouite/emerald-necklace

name: delapouite/empty-chessboard

name: delapouite/empty-metal-bucket-handle

name: delapouite/empty-wood-bucket-handle

name: delapouite/european-flag

name: delapouite/exit-door

name: delapouite/expand

name: delapouite/expense

name: delapouite/eye-of-horus

name: delapouite/eye-target

name: delapouite/f-clef

name: delapouite/face-to-face

name: delapouite/factory-arm

name: delapouite/fairy-wings

name: delapouite/falcon-moon

name: delapouite/falling-bomb

name: delapouite/falling-rocks

Rocks going down a cliff in a dangerous avalanche.
Can often block road access during days.

name: delapouite/falling-star

A countryside worker taking care of crops and cattle.
Agricultural work on his land is easier with a tractor than with only a pitchfork.

name: delapouite/fast-backward-button

name: delapouite/feline
description: A symbol of all the big cats out there: lions, tigers, panthers…

name: delapouite/female-legs
description: Resting legs of a sitting woman barefoot or with light stocking.

name: delapouite/female-vampire
description: A young version of Elizabeth Bathory or Wednesday Addams.

name: delapouite/female
description: Gender specific sign for women and girls.

name: delapouite/fencer
description: During fencing, two competitors in suit attempt to score by making contact with their opponent with their rapier style sword.

name: delapouite/fern
description: What's going on between these 2 ferns?

name: delapouite/fertilizer-bag
description: Special product to increase the growth of plants and increase harvests.

name: delapouite/fez
description: A north African red conic hat with a tassel.

name: delapouite/figurehead
description: Ocean godess at the bow of a wooden ship.

name: delapouite/files
description:
Blank paper documents spread in a random fashion on a messy desk.
These cards need to be filled with tasks.

name: delapouite/film-projector
description: An old movie projector to display big pictures on the screen of a cinema theater.

name: delapouite/film-spool
description: Round spinner to roll a movie around.

name: delapouite/film-strip
description: A spooled roll used by the cinema industry to project movies.

name: delapouite/finch

name: delapouite/finger-print

name: delapouite/fingernail
description: This strong transparent piece protect the tips of fingers.

name: delapouite/finish-line
description: The end of the race is near, the winner just has to cross the line.

name: delapouite/fire-extinguisher

description: When Mario or Luigi blow on the petals, it casts fire balls.

name: delapouite/fire-gem
description: With this precious artifact, a magician can summon fire spirits and use flames to fight enemies.

name: delapouite/fire-shrine
description: A simple magic flame to invoke fire spirits.

name: delapouite/fire-spell-cast
description: A magic power starting from a spark and ending in a formidable arson.

name: delapouite/fireplace
description: Put wood logs in this to warm the house during cold periods.

name: delapouite/firewall
description: A hot barrier with no way to go through without protection.

name: delapouite/first-aid-kit
description: When there's an injury, medicines are needed.

name: delapouite/fish-bucket
description: These dead animals are the result of a fishing afternoon.

name: delapouite/fish-eggs
description: On the bottom of the river, dozens of eggs will become tiny fish.

name: delapouite/fish-escape
description: This courageous goldfish is about to explore the waterless world.

name: delapouite/fish-monster
description: A reptilian beast that can breath underwater and provide good advices to adventurers near waterfalls.

name: delapouite/fish-scales

name: delapouite/fish-smoking

name: delapouite/fishing-boat
description: Small motorised boat harvesting fish from rivers and oceans by dragging big nets.

name: delapouite/fishing-lure
description: A fake prey to trick hungry fish.

name: delapouite/fishing-pole
description: This fishing rod has a hook to capture hungry submarine animals if you attach the right bait.

name: delapouite/fishing-spoon
description: Sharp hooks attached to a small piece of shiny metal that attracts fish predators.

name: delapouite/fishing
description: Capture fish with a hook and a line.

name: delapouite/flag-objective
description: Follow the indications to reach your goal. Almost like playing golf.

name: delapouite/flail
description:
A one handed flail consisting of a spiky ball attach to a wooden haft by a chain.
Favorite weapon of Simon Belmont.

name: delapouite/flamethrower-soldier
description: An infantry man burning everything on the battle field with high pressure napalm.

name: delapouite/flamethrower
description: An incendiary device projecting stream of napalm.

name: delapouite/flamingo
description: A pink bird with long legs mainly living in flocks in the swamps of Florida. It loves eating shrimps.

name: delapouite/flanged-mace
description: A heavy club with reinforced flanges in metal.

name: delapouite/flashlight
description: Hand device spreading light into darkness to search the correct safe path.

name: delapouite/flat-platform
description: A square ground with a small step.

name: delapouite/flat-tire

name: delapouite/flatfish
description: A plaice can slip under narrow traps and avoid fishermen's nets.

name: delapouite/flax
description: A fiber crop also knows as linseed, used to produce linen clothes.

name: delapouite/fleur-de-lys
description: This flower is the royal symbol of French kings.

name: delapouite/flexible-lamp
description: In the shadows of a dark office, a bit of light near the desk is mandatory to keep writing.

name: delapouite/flint-spark
description: The chock between these two rocks will produce the flame needed to lit the fire.

name: delapouite/flip-flops
description: Casual sandals to wear during summer on the beach. They are called thongs in Australia.

name: delapouite/floating-ghost
description: A goofy angel helping poor souls to reach better places.

name: delapouite/floating-platforms
description: A piece of ground high in the sky. Perfect for combats during a tournament.

name: delapouite/floating-tentacles
description: This one-eye jellyfish is a deadly oculus in a narrow corridor.

name: delapouite/flood
description: This house is unfortunately under water.

name: delapouite/floor-hatch
description:
A sudden man size hole in the ground ready to swallow victims that unfortunately activated the mechanism.
It leads to a deadly pit below.

name: delapouite/floor-polisher
description: To keep everything shiny even after dirty shoe steps.

name: delapouite/flower-emblem
description: A flower with symmetrical petals around the core.

name: delapouite/flower-hat
description: A pretty hat to spread happiness during spring.

name: delapouite/flower-star
description: A lotus with well balanced corolla composed of 8 petals evenly distributed around a small round stigma.

name: delapouite/flute
description: A woodwind instrument. Blow inside and cap the holes to make a nice tunes.

name: delapouite/fly
description: A flying dot which likes to annoy you by circling around your ears or sitting on your food.

name: delapouite/flying-beetle
description: This winged scarab is a precious amulet.

name: delapouite/flying-fox
description: A zip-line practitioner along a metal cable.

name: delapouite/flying-target
description: Look at the sky and try to reach those objectives floating with the wind. This training will turn useful to hunt real birds or flying creatures.

name: delapouite/fog-light
description: A special indicator on a car dahsboard when the weather is bad.

name: delapouite/fog
description: A low cloud preventing vision, like in Silent Hill.

name: delapouite/food-truck
description: The perfect spot to eat junk food during the lunch break.

name: delapouite/foot-plaster
description: Bandages after a bad injury at the leg. Toes seem fine, but the ankle may be broken.

name: delapouite/footy-field
description: Australian soccer, a spicy mix of European soccer and rugby played in an oval stadium.

name: delapouite/forearm
description: Extremity of the superior limb, can be covered with gauntlets.

name: delapouite/forest-camp
description: A tent near at pine tree to stay for a while in the calm.

name: delapouite/forest
description: Impenetrable patch of pine trees in the country. This forest does not seem haunted.

name: delapouite/fork-knife-spoon
description: This trio of metal sticks just need a plate and be placed on the table of a restaurant.

name: delapouite/forklift
description: A small industrial truck to move heavy crates in a warehouse.

name: delapouite/foundry-bucket
description: High temperature metal being poured in a steelworks factory.

name: delapouite/fox-tail
description: Tails, Sonic's friend, has two of this mighty fire hair parts.

name: delapouite/france
description: Country in Western Europe with the Alps on the South East.

name: delapouite/freemasonry
description: Fraternal organisation secretly ruling the world.

name: delapouite/french-fries
description: A Belgian dish made of potatoes cooked in oil.

name: delapouite/fried-eggs
description: Ready for breakfast, just waiting for the bacon and cheese.

name: delapouite/frisbee
description: A plastic disc you throw on the beach for fun or during golf competitions.

name: delapouite/frog-foot
description: This sticky foot has a perfect grip to climb wall like geckos.

name: delapouite/frog-prince
description: This ugly toad can be transformed back to its original human nature by a simple kiss from a princess.

name: delapouite/frozen-body
description: This person is trapped in a giant ice cube that will never melt.

name: delapouite/frozen-ring

column5: a musketeers apology praising team work to defeat foes."

Just turn the wrench clockwise and the cog will fit the right position in the engine.

name: lorc/automatic-sas

name: lorc/barbed-nails

name: lorc/barbed-spear

Almost the same principal has a fishing hook.
When you remove the rip from the flesh, it creates lots more damages than the other way around.

name: lorc/barbed-star

name: lorc/barbed-sun
